How to Present Xtrata in Competition

When crafting your submission (pitch deck, demo, video, poster):
	1.	“Problem → Solution” Narrative
Build the hook around the limitation of pointer-based NFTs and how Xtrata’s model elevates permanence and composability.
	2.	Live Demo + SDK Walkthrough
Show an inscribed work, its dependency graph, and reconstruction via tooling — ideally with metrics.
	3.	Integration Story
Early integrations with marketplaces or builder tools show adoption and ecosystem traction.
	4.	Measurable Outcomes
Public dashboards, reliability metrics, integration logs, or community interest signups add credibility.

